<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

        <style>

            .center{display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 95px; height: 95px} .body-heading { text-align: center; } h1, h2 {
            color: red; } .button { border-radius: 2px; } .button a { padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #ffc107; border-radius: 2px; font-family:
            Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1e56a0; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }

        </style>

    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="body-heading">
            <img src="http://app.high-view-studios.co.uk/HighViewStudios/templates/logo.jpg" class="center" />
            <h1><strong>High-View Studios</strong></h1>
        </div>

        <p>Dear {{name}} ({{email}}),</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with High-View Studios.</p>
        <p>A place that meets all your technicial needs.</p>

        <p>You will need to verify your email to use the ViewHelp system and to access your invoices and reciepts.</p>

        <p>Your login information is as follows: </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Username: please use the email you see above</li>
            <li>Password: please use the password you have provided</li><br />
        </ul>

        <p>Also, Please click the buttom below to verify your email:</p>

        <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="button" bgcolor="#ffc107">
                                <a class="link" href="http://localhost:3000/membership/emailverified/{{id}}/{{email}}" target="_blank">
                                    VERIFY NOW
                                </a>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <br />

        <p>Regards,</p>

        <p><strong>High-View Studios</strong></p>

    </body>
